  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They concentrated them from one place to the other place, and we were-- they brought them to our place.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In our house there were a few families living, and by some other people, because there wasn't place where to a few, a few families in one house.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And at this time they took out-- in Podhajce, we hear the next day, because we were still somebody was there in, in contact with Podhajce.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they took-- they killed 1,300 people, which I have a monument which I'll show you later on.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And this Yom Kippur, they came into our shul in Podhajce and they took out the rabbi and the other [? prayers, ?] and placed where there was garbage-- a garbage hall.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They took them out in their prayer shawls and they killed them there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And also in this place, it was called old city, they may-- they killed 1,300 people in this day.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The next day they were talking that the earth was like, like moving.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Because they, because there were a lot of people who still lived there, and they were put into the grave alive.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I heard about this, yeah, because we had relatives there in Podhajce, and we were still in our city.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They brought to our city those other from the other one.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And six weeks later was another aksia.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not in Zawalow.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Six weeks later was the other aksia.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No, by the other aksia they, it was in the old city, that they killed the 1,300 people.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And this first--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, in Yom Kippur they did this thing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Six weeks later, they brought all from Zawalow, all the people, to Podhajce, and they made the ghetto in Podhajce.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The ghetto in Podhajce-- no, they brought us all in to the, to Podhajce.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
